data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT*** Step into this darling fresh new home that has been carefully and stylishly updated for its new owners.  Feel the crisp, clean, fresh, new look, ready for you to make it your own!  No carpet,. All flooring covered with premium laminate wood-look w/pad, bright, open concept from great room to kitchen with new, convenient island space and countertops.  Kitchen cabinets are soft-close.  Both bathrooms have updates and all new hardware throughout the home for a great sleek look. All the windows are newer vinyl, new drywall in basement and the whole house has been freshly painted.  Original and usable wood burning fireplace downstairs. New electric wiring, air ducts and air conditioning unit cleaned. Attached 2-car garage with additional workspace. Walk out on to a pretty, freshly painted, covered gazebo and enjoy quiet sunsets or start your day in this peaceful spot.  Seller has just seeded the backyard so expect a nice carpet of green back there! Too many upgrades and improvements to mention here,  See attached list.  This home is ready & waiting for you! Seller has had an inspection done and report is available to buyers. KeyBank offers an additional $5,000 to qualified home buyers to assist with closing costs!
